modules.description: This module implements GPU-accelerated 2D rendering operations using OpenGL ES 2.0, including texture management, path filling/stroking, and triangle rendering. It works with vector paths, vertex buffers, and GPU textures, supporting operations like antialiasing, scissoring, and compositing. Concrete use cases include rendering vector graphics, UI elements, and dynamic 2D visuals in applications with OpenGL ES 2.0 support.

This module implements GPU-accelerated 2D rendering using OpenGL ES 2.0, providing operations for texture management, path filling and stroking, and triangle rendering. It works with vector paths, vertex buffers, and GPU textures, supporting features like antialiasing, scissoring, and compositing. Use cases include rendering vector graphics, UI elements, and dynamic 2D visuals in OpenGL ES 2.0-compatible applications.
